I've inserted a few documents into

00:00:06.059 --> 00:00:10.364
the patient's collection to help me demonstrate the querying capabilities.

00:00:10.365 --> 00:00:14.609
We have the usual steps of creating a Mongo client,

00:00:14.609 --> 00:00:19.829
getting the database, and getting a collection.

00:00:19.829 --> 00:00:24.989
Then I have the various ways of using the Find method.

00:00:24.989 --> 00:00:27.329
Find with an argument,

00:00:27.329 --> 00:00:30.464
find with a logical operator,

00:00:30.464 --> 00:00:33.524
and find with an array field,

00:00:33.524 --> 00:00:40.449
and also a sub-document then I have the sort or here,

00:00:40.909 --> 00:00:46.579
