00:01:20.944 --> 00:01:23.179
the sorted set of documents are here,

00:01:23.180 --> 00:01:28.160
he count, the limit and finally the combination.

00:01:28.159 --> 00:01:34.629
There you go. You just learned how to query documents using the Mongo driver.

